    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been truly loved? This beauty is in great shape and ready for all your upcoming adventures! It runs super smoothly and has been really well-maintained, so you can just hop in and hit the road with total peace of mind. I\u2019ve genuinely enjoyed every mile in this car, and I know you will too. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
