      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the legendary S54 inline-six, delivering 333hp with a crisp 8,000 RPM redline. The VANOS system has been addressed, and the subframe reinforced\u2014critical preventative measures for this chassis. It retains a tactile 6-speed manual transmission with short-throw precision. The suspension geometry remains tight, utilizing Bilstein dampers for improved rebound and compression over stock. While the aesthetic shows minor patina consistent with its age, the mechanical vitals are robust, featuring consistent compression across all cylinders and a limited-slip differential that locks predictably under load. A purist\u2019s spec ready for the canyons.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Used sedan. Reliable runner. Clean interior. Minimal body wear. Passed inspection.",
