    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in really solid shape, ready for many more miles of adventures! It drives smoothly and has been well-loved over the years. I\u2019m super excited for someone else to enjoy it as much as I have. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 2950.0,
