    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Available for the discerning driver is this 1997 Toyota Supra Turbo, featuring the legendary 2JZ-GTE power plant. This A80 retains its factory twin-sequential turbocharger configuration, delivering linear power through the sought-after Getrag V160 6-speed manual gearbox. The drivetrain is anchored by a Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution. Mechanically sound, the vehicle exhibits consistent compression across all cylinders and a clean cooling system. The four-wheel independent double-wishbone suspension provides precise turn-in, while the factory braking system remains sharp. A mechanically honest example of Japanese over-engineering, ready for spirited driving or as a robust platform for further tuning.",
